n 2024 23:01:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-say-no-change-in-policy-of-targeting-hamas-leaders-despite-hostage-deaths/0000018d-4253-d35c-a39f-ea5b514d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国和以色列在加沙战争中敲定重大军用飞机交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/u-s-and-israel-finalize-major-military-aircraft-deals-amid-gaza-war/0000018d-4234-d35c-a39f-ea7e5b8c0000</link><description>随着加沙战争进入第五个月，与真主党全面战争的准备工作正在进行中，以色列预计将利用美国援助资金购买两个中队的战斗机和一个中队的攻击直升机</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 21:05:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/u-s-and-israel-finalize-major-military-aircraft-deals-amid-gaza-war/0000018d-4234-d35c-a39f-ea7e5b8c0000</guid></item><item><title>共和党人正在研究内塔尼亚胡如何打击拜登的战后加沙计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/republicans-are-looking-at-netanyahu-for-how-to-combat-bidens-post-war-gaza-plans/0000018d-4162-d35c-a39f-eb7a4a6e0000</link><description>随着拜登政府敦促以色列结束对加沙的地面入侵，并展望巴勒斯坦权力机构掌管的可能未来，美国共和党人正在陷入共和党风格的困境</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 20:10:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/republicans-are-looking-at-netanyahu-for-how-to-combat-bidens-post-war-gaza-plans/0000018d-4162-d35c-a39f-eb7a4a6e0000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列和哈马斯推进人质协议，停火仍然是争论的焦点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/cease-fire-remains-bone-of-contention-as-israel-and-hamas-advance-toward-hostage-deal/0000018d-41b7-d02c-a79f-43bf13c30000</link><description>据熟悉谈判的消息人士透露，双方已就协议的大部分条款达成基本协议，“但需要解决的核心问题是哈马斯坚持的全面停火问题”</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 19:12:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/cease-fire-remains-bone-of-contention-as-israel-and-hamas-advance-toward-hostage-deal/0000018d-41b7-d02c-a79f-43bf13c30000</guid></item><item><title>是的，与杀人犯和平相处</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/yes-peace-is-made-with-murderers/0000018d-4133-d02c-a79f-43bb6cc80000</link><description>大多数解决民族冲突的协议都无法经受住时间的考验。对那些成功人士的研究揭示了其中的秘密：他们都是从监狱里出来的。以色列需要在加沙战争“后一天”考虑这一点</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 18:55:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/yes-peace-is-made-with-murderers/0000018d-4133-d02c-a79f-43bb6cc80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡办公室同意“泄露”总理抨击卡塔尔的录音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-okayed-leaked-recording-of-him-bashing-qatar/0000018d-4160-d35c-a39f-eb7af9c60000</link><description>如果内塔尼亚胡总理认为这符合以色列的最佳利益和外交政策，这并不是内塔尼亚胡办公室第一次批准有关敏感安全问题的报道</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 18:01:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-okayed-leaked-recording-of-him-bashing-qatar/0000018d-4160-d35c-a39f-eb7af9c60000</guid></item><item><title>东耶路撒冷居民在一月初西岸袭击中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/east-jerusalem-resident-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-west-bank-attack-earlier-in-january/0000018d-4160-dc44-a5bf-c9f600be0000</link><description>42 岁的拉拉·坦努斯 (Lara Tannous) 医生在耶路撒冷一家医院担任药剂师。大约三周前，她在奥夫拉社区附近的约旦河西岸枪击事件中被枪杀，东耶路撒冷居民阿马尔·曼苏尔 (Amar Mansour)，32 岁也被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 17:11:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/east-jerusalem-resident-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-west-bank-attack-earlier-in-january/0000018d-4160-dc44-a5bf-c9f600be0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列“Fauda”明星在加沙受重伤，讲述爆炸事件，呼吁释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fauda-star-seriously-wounded-in-gaza-recounts-blast-calls-for-hostages-release/0000018d-40e3-dc44-a5bf-c8f781e80000</link><description>演员兼歌手伊丹·阿梅迪住院近三周，他在以色列主流新闻媒体现场直播的新闻发布会上表示，他希望尽快恢复表演和拍摄</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 16:09:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fauda-star-seriously-wounded-in-gaza-recounts-blast-calls-for-hostages-release/0000018d-40e3-dc44-a5bf-c8f781e80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列摩萨德否认内塔尼亚胡盟友将司法改革抗议领导人与哈马斯联系起来的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/mossad-denies-netanyahu-allys-claims-about-judicial-overhaul-protester-links-with-hamas/0000018d-4015-dc44-a5bf-c8b74c940000</link><description>塔利·戈特利夫在社交媒体上发帖称，美国拦截了哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔与以色列政府反对者之间的通话，摩萨德已召集该反对者参加会议</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 15:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/mossad-denies-netanyahu-allys-claims-about-judicial-overhaul-protester-links-with-hamas/0000018d-4015-dc44-a5bf-c8b74c940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对周五国际法院对加沙种族灭绝指控的临时裁决有何期待？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/what-can-israel-expect-in-tomorrows-icj-interim-ruling-on-the-gaza-genocide-charge/0000018d-40bc-d35c-a39f-eafe6d450000</link><description>南非在国际法院指控以色列犯有种族灭绝罪。法院会要求立即停火吗？以色列官员会因煽动而受到惩罚吗？裁决将如何执行？</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 15:12:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/what-can-israel-expect-in-tomorrows-icj-interim-ruling-on-the-gaza-genocide-charge/0000018d-40bc-d35c-a39f-eafe6d450000</guid></item><item><title>在国际法院裁决之前，以色列解密文件以证明其保护平民的努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/ahead-of-icj-ruling-israel-declassifies-documents-to-prove-efforts-to-protect-civilians/0000018d-40d0-d35c-a39f-eadac21b0000</link><description>据《纽约时报》报道，在国际法院就南非对以色列提出的种族灭绝指控作出临时裁决的前一天，以色列解密文件以证明其意图</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 14:48:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/ahead-of-icj-ruling-israel-declassifies-documents-to-prove-efforts-to-protect-civilians/0000018d-40d0-d35c-a39f-eadac21b0000</guid></item><item><title>关于以色列-哈马斯人质释放过程的关键问答：“辛瓦尔很高兴为释放囚犯而死”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/q-a-on-israel-hamas-hostage-release-process-sinwar-is-happy-to-die-to-free-prisoners/0000018d-40ab-d35c-a39f-eafb67aa0000</link><description>根据我与加沙哈马斯领导人间接谈判的经验，这是他的观点。但他也认为，战后他将走出隧道并继续掌权。以下是有关此事的几个常见关键问题</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 14:27:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/q-a-on-israel-hamas-hostage-release-process-sinwar-is-happy-to-die-to-free-prisoners/0000018d-40ab-d35c-a39f-eafb67aa0000</guid></item><item><title>“你怎么能赢得一场强加给你的战争呢？”加沙日记作者与死亡作斗争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-can-you-win-a-war-that-was-forced-on-you-gaza-diarists-grapple-with-death/0000018d-3c42-d07d-a79d-fde766f10000</link><description>由于国际媒体基本上被禁止进入加沙地带，加沙作家正在出版战争日记并填补空白</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 13:58:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-can-you-win-a-war-that-was-forced-on-you-gaza-diarists-grapple-with-death/0000018d-3c42-d07d-a79d-fde766f10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列科学家发现焦虑与低睾酮水平之间缺失联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-scientists-discover-missing-link-between-anxiety-and-low-testosterone/0000018d-40b2-d02c-a79f-43bb44b50000</link><description>众所周知，雄性激素缺乏与焦虑有关，现在我们知道了其中的原因。如果你的老鼠患有麻痹性焦虑症，注射一针睾酮可能会给他带来奇迹，但在未来，这一发现提出了一种新方法</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 13:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-scientists-discover-missing-link-between-anxiety-and-low-testosterone/0000018d-40b2-d02c-a79f-43bb44b50000</guid></item><item><title>先是拜登，现在是卡塔尔：内塔尼亚胡正在创造敌人，以使他的中东永远战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/first-biden-now-qatar-netanyahu-is-creating-nemeses-to-get-his-mideast-forever-war/0000018d-4061-d02c-a79f-43fb9cc20000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡称卡塔尔代表以色列人质的调解角色“有问题”，这将他的战时行为推向了新的低点——这对一个不理解“公共礼仪”或“接受责任”等术语的人来说是有道理的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 13:29:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/first-biden-now-qatar-netanyahu-is-creating-nemeses-to-get-his-mideast-forever-war/0000018d-4061-d02c-a79f-43fb9cc20000</guid></item><item><title>柏林展览聚焦加沙最年轻的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/berlin-exhibit-spotlights-youngest-hostage-held-in-gaza/0000018d-40a2-dc44-a5bf-c8b6be5f0000</link><description>为了纪念 Kfir Bibas 的一周岁生日，柏林举办了一场展览，汇集了献给与家人一起被绑架到加沙的红发男婴的作品</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 13:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/berlin-exhibit-spotlights-youngest-hostage-held-in-gaza/0000018d-40a2-dc44-a5bf-c8b6be5f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列为拯救约旦河西岸迈出一小步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-takes-one-small-step-to-rescue-the-west-bank/0000018d-407c-d02c-a79f-43ff487b0000</link><description>以色列周日批准向巴勒斯坦权力机构提供资金的计划是一个良好的开端，但不足以使西岸免遭经济破坏</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 12:09:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-takes-one-small-step-to-rescue-the-west-bank/0000018d-407c-d02c-a79f-43ff487b0000</guid></item><item><title>只有巴解组织脱离哈马斯，才会有巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/therell-only-be-a-palestinian-state-if-the-plo-disengages-from-hamas/0000018d-3fa7-d35c-a39f-bfff192c0000</link><description>巴解组织准备承认对整个巴勒斯坦的“历史性权利”，包括难民返回的权利。另一方面，哈马斯坚持继续对以色列进行武装斗争</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 11:53:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/therell-only-be-a-palestinian-state-if-the-plo-disengages-from-hamas/0000018d-3fa7-d35c-a39f-bfff192c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>